29|16|And (remember) Ibrahim when he said to his people: "Worship Allah, and have Taqwa of Him, that is better for you if you know."
29|17|You worship besides Allah only idols, and you only invent falsehood. Verily, those whom you worship besides Allah have no power to give you provision, so seek from Allah your provision, and worship Him, and be grateful to Him. To Him you will be brought back.
29|18|And if you deny, then nations before you have denied. And the duty of the Messenger is only to convey plainly."
29|19|See they not how Allah originates the creation, then repeats it. Verily, that is easy for Allah.
